title: Malwarebytes for Android Premium 3.1.0.11
description:
Malwarebytes for Android Premium 3.1.0.11 Full [4REALTORRENTZ]

Description:

The world’s most popular anti-malware technology has gone mobile! Malwarebytes for Android protects your phone or tablet from malware, ransomware, adware, and unauthorized surveillance—all in real time.

To existing Malwarebytes Anti-Malware customers: Malwarebytes for Android provides the same features you love, such as scanning and remediation, for free. The included Premium trial lets you sample additional features for 30 days, after which Malwarebytes for Android will revert to a free version.

SUPPORT FORUM > Malwarebytes for Android
•For help on how to use our products, visit support at: https://support.malwarebytes.com/

Malwarebytes for Android:

• Detects ransomware and malware before they can infect your Android.
• Scans your apps for malicious code, Potentially Unwanted Programs (PUPs), or adware to keep your Android running smooth.
• Automatically detects if a malicious link is found in an incoming text message. 
• Detects malicious links in any text, including email, messenger services such asor Whatsapp, or websites, through on-demand scans.
• Identifies applications that track your location, monitor your calls, or cost you extra money in hidden fees
